# Domain layer

Путь: `app/Domain/{BC}/{Entity|VO|Event|Service|Repository}`.

Naming: English only. No Russian. No transliteration.

## Allowed

- Aggregates / entities with invariants and domain methods
- Value objects, domain events, domain services, repository **interfaces**
- Depend only on `App\Domain\{same BC}\...` and `App\Shared\...`

## Forbidden

- Import `App\Application\...`, `App\Infrastructure\...`, Eloquent, HTTP, frameworks
- Call handlers / use cases / repositories of **another** BC
- Import entities/services/repositories of another BC
- Mutate another BC’s state synchronously

Cross-BC identity only via `EntityId` (or own VO id), never via foreign aggregates.

## Cross-BC mutations

Only through **domain events** published by the owning aggregate. Another BC reacts later (application event listener / policy) — never via direct method/handler call.

```php
// ❌ BAD — Workshop calls Order domain/application
$order->markReady();
$completeReceptionHandler->handle(...);

// ✅ GOOD — Workshop records own event; Order reacts via event flow
$this->record(new ProductionCompleted($this->id, $this->orderItemId));
```

## Structure

| Folder | Role |
|--------|------|
| `Entity` | Aggregates and entities |
| `VO` | Value objects / enums |
| `Event` | Domain events (`DomainEvent`) |
| `Service` | Domain logic that does not belong to one entity |
| `Repository` | Persistence ports (interfaces only) |
